      "content": "The board isn't just looking for \"safer,\" they're looking for \"responsible.\" They've pointed out that your \"stirring the pot\" often means leaning into racialized tropes that play on fear within specific communities. If we move to Ethos-Core, we solve the legal and ethical risks entirely. Are you saying that staying competitive requires us to keep using those specific, controversial demographic triggers?",
